<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>StarckKey — Gestion d'Agenda Immobilier</title>
<!-- ✅ Client ID PayPal Sandbox configuré -->
<script src="https://www.paypal.com/sdk/js?client-id=ASneTpBhaCtOrjU21OtzSpu9VN1kzVFkzS8P_W89BFCO_7kke3tZiT3Gz9i4ntctcJEn6x7F1aFTVUmk&currency=EUR&locale=fr_FR&components=buttons,hosted-fields&intent=capture"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#F4F6FB;--surface:#fff;--ink:#0D1B3E;--ink-mid:#2D3F6B;--ink-mute:#5A6E99;--ink-lt:#8FA0C0;
  --border:#C8D3E8;--border-l:#DDE5F2;--navy:#1C3A7A;--navy-hov:#142D61;--navy-dk:#0D1E4A;--navy-bg:#E8EEFB;
  --gold:#C9A227;--gold-hov:#A88318;--gold-lt:#E8C84A;--gold-pale:#FDF4D4;--gold-dk:#7A5E08;
  --silver:#8A96A8;--silver-bg:#F0F2F6;--green:#1A6B3A;--green-bg:#E6F4EC;--red:#C0392B;--red-bg:#FFF0EE;--nav-h:64px;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden;line-height:1.6}
@media(pointer:fine){
  body{cursor:none}
  #cur{position:fixed;width:8px;height:8px;background:var(--navy);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:transform .12s}
  #cur-ring{position:fixed;width:28px;height:28px;border:1.5px solid var(--navy);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9998;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:all .22s;opacity:.3}
  body:has(a:hover) #cur,body:has(button:hover) #cur{transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(2.5)}
  body:has(a:hover) #cur-ring,body:has(button:hover) #cur-ring{width:44px;height:44px;opacity:.12}
}
#heartbeat{position:fixed;bottom:22px;right:22px;z-index:500;width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);animation:hb 3s ease-in-out infinite;pointer-events:none}
@keyframes hb{0%,100%{opacity:.3;transform:scale(1)}50%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1.6)}}

/* ══ NAV ══ */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;height:var(–nav-h);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:0 56px;background:rgba(244,246,251,.97);border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);transition:box-shadow .3s;backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}
nav.scrolled{box-shadow:0 2px 24px rgba(28,58,122,.1)}
.logo{font-size:16px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;color:var(–navy)}
.logo em{font-style:normal;color:var(–gold)}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none}
.nav-links a{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(–ink-mute);text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(–navy)}
.nav-cta{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fff;background:var(–navy);padding:11px 22px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;white-space:nowrap;transition:background .2s,transform .1s}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk)}
.burger{display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;cursor:pointer;padding:8px;background:none;border:none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
.burger span{display:block;width:22px;height:2px;background:var(–navy);transition:all .25s;border-radius:1px}
.burger.open span:nth-child(1){transform:translateY(7px) rotate(45deg)}
.burger.open span:nth-child(2){opacity:0}
.burger.open span:nth-child(3){transform:translateY(-7px) rotate(-45deg)}
.mob-menu{display:none;position:fixed;top:var(–nav-h);left:0;right:0;background:var(–surface);border-bottom:3px solid var(–gold);padding:8px 24px 24px;z-index:199;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(28,58,122,.12)}
.mob-menu.open{display:flex}
.mob-menu a{display:block;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:var(–ink-mid);text-decoration:none;padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border-l)}
.mob-menu a:last-of-type{border:none}
.mob-menu a:hover{color:var(–navy)}
.mob-cta{margin-top:16px;background:var(–navy)!important;color:#fff!important;text-align:center;padding:15px!important;font-weight:700!important;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;border-radius:4px;border:none!important}

/* ══ HERO ══ */
.hero{min-height:100vh;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;align-items:center;padding:calc(var(–nav-h)+72px) 56px 80px;gap:72px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero-grid{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;background-image:linear-gradient(var(–border-l) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,var(–border-l) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;opacity:.6;mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 90% at 50% 50%,black 10%,transparent 75%)}
.hero-left{position:relative;z-index:1}
.hero-over{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–navy);margin-bottom:28px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .6s .1s forwards}
.hero-over::before{content:’’;width:20px;height:2px;background:var(–gold);flex-shrink:0}
h1{font-size:clamp(38px,4.5vw,72px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.0;letter-spacing:-2px;color:var(–ink);margin-bottom:24px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .6s .2s forwards}
h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(–gold);display:block}
.hero-body{font-size:15px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;color:var(–ink-mid);max-width:420px;margin-bottom:44px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .6s .35s forwards}
.hero-acts{display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .6s .5s forwards}
.btn-main{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fff;background:var(–navy);padding:15px 32px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;transition:background .2s,transform .1s;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;cursor:pointer;border:none;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif}
.btn-main:hover{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk)}
.btn-main:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
.btn-out{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(–ink-mute);background:transparent;padding:15px 28px;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;transition:border-color .2s,color .2s,transform .1s}
.btn-out:hover{border-color:var(–navy);color:var(–navy)}
.hero-right{position:relative;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .7s .65s forwards}
.fl-badge{position:absolute;background:var(–surface);border:1px solid var(–border);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(28,58,122,.1);padding:11px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;z-index:2;border-radius:6px}
.fl-1{top:-16px;right:-16px;animation:floatY 5s 1s ease-in-out infinite}
.fl-2{bottom:-16px;left:-16px;animation:floatY 5s 2s ease-in-out infinite}
.fl-icon{font-size:16px}
.fl-text strong{display:block;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(–ink)}
.fl-text span{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–ink-mute);letter-spacing:1px}
.hcard{background:var(–surface);border:1px solid var(–border);border-radius:10px;padding:32px;position:relative;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(28,58,122,.1);animation:floatY 6s ease-in-out infinite}
.hcard::before{content:’’;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–navy),var(–gold));border-radius:10px 10px 0 0}
.card-lbl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–ink-mute);margin-bottom:18px}
.card-agent{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:18px;padding-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border-l)}
.av{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:var(–navy);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.ag-name{font-weight:600;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:2px;color:var(–ink)}
.ag-role{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–ink-mute);letter-spacing:1px}
.cstats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:18px}
.sbox{background:var(–bg);padding:12px;border:1px solid var(–border-l);border-radius:4px}
.sv{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;margin-bottom:3px;letter-spacing:-1px;color:var(–ink)}
.sv span{font-size:12px;color:var(–gold);font-weight:500}
.slbl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–ink-mute)}
.sched-ttl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–ink-mute);margin-bottom:10px}
.sched-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border-l)}
.sched-row:last-child{border:none}
.sdot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.da{background:var(–navy)}.db{background:var(–gold)}.dc{background:var(–ink-lt)}
.stime{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–ink-mute);min-width:40px}
.stxt{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;flex:1;color:var(–ink)}
.sbadge{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:3px}
.bok{background:var(–green-bg);color:var(–green)}.bpend{background:var(–gold-pale);color:var(–gold-dk)}

/* ══ MARQUEE ══ */
.mq-wrap{background:var(–navy-dk);padding:13px 0;overflow:hidden}
.mq-track{display:flex;white-space:nowrap;animation:marquee 32s linear infinite}
.mq-item{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:0 32px;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}
.mq-item span{color:var(–gold);font-size:14px}

/* ══ SHARED ══ */
.s-over{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–navy);margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.s-over::before{content:’’;width:16px;height:2px;background:var(–gold);flex-shrink:0}
.s-title{font-size:clamp(27px,2.8vw,48px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-1.5px;color:var(–ink)}
.s-title em{font-style:normal;color:var(–gold)}
.s-head{margin-bottom:56px}

/* ══ FEATURES ══ */
.features{padding:112px 56px;background:var(–surface)}
.feats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(–border-l)}
.feat{background:var(–surface);padding:40px 32px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:background .25s;cursor:default}
.feat:hover{background:var(–bg)}
.feat-bar{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:0;height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–navy),var(–gold));transition:width .4s}
.feat:hover .feat-bar{width:100%}
.feat-num{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(–ink-lt);margin-bottom:24px;transition:color .25s}
.feat:hover .feat-num{color:var(–navy)}
.feat-ico{font-size:22px;margin-bottom:14px;display:block}
.feat-ttl{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(–ink)}
.feat-desc{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;color:var(–ink-mid)}

/* ══ PROOF ══ */
.proof{background:var(–navy-dk);padding:88px 56px}
.proof-hd{text-align:center;margin-bottom:52px}
.proof-hd .s-over{justify-content:center;color:rgba(201,162,39,.7)}
.proof-hd .s-over::before{background:var(–gold);opacity:.6}
.proof-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden}
.proof-item{padding:44px 24px;text-align:center;position:relative;border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
.proof-item:last-child{border-right:none}
.proof-n{font-size:52px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:-2px}
.proof-lbl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}
.proof-bar{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;height:2px;background:var(–gold);width:0;transition:width .9s cubic-bezier(.76,0,.24,1)}
.proof-item.visible .proof-bar{width:100%}

/* ══ PRICING ══ */
.pricing{padding:112px 56px;background:var(–bg)}
.pricing-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(–ink-mid);margin-top:12px;max-width:560px;line-height:1.7}
.pricing-sub strong{color:var(–navy);font-weight:600}
.plbl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–ink-mute);margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:20px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border)}
.plans{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px}
.plan{background:var(–surface);border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:8px;padding:36px 28px;position:relative;transition:transform .3s,box-shadow .3s,border-color .3s}
.plan:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(28,58,122,.1);border-color:var(–navy)}
.plan.pop{border-color:var(–gold);background:var(–navy)}
.plan.pop:hover{box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(28,58,122,.3)}
.plan.pop::before{content:‘POPULAIRE’;position:absolute;top:-1px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk);font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:5px 14px;border-radius:0 0 4px 4px;white-space:nowrap;font-weight:800}
.plan-tag{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–ink-mute);margin-bottom:18px}
.plan.pop .plan-tag{color:var(–gold-lt)}
.plan-price{font-size:48px;font-weight:800;line-height:1;color:var(–ink);margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:2px;letter-spacing:-2px}
.plan.pop .plan-price{color:#fff}
.plan-price sup{font-size:20px;padding-top:8px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0}
.plan-price small{font-size:16px;font-weight:300;align-self:flex-end;padding-bottom:4px;letter-spacing:0}
.plan-per{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(–ink-mute);margin-bottom:24px;padding-bottom:20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border-l)}
.plan.pop .plan-per{color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.1)}
.plan-feats{list-style:none;margin-bottom:28px}
.plan-feats li{font-size:13px;color:var(–ink-mid);padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border-l);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px}
.plan-feats li::before{content:‘✓’;color:var(–navy);flex-shrink:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700}
.plan.pop .plan-feats li{color:rgba(255,255,255,.72);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.1)}
.plan.pop .plan-feats li::before{color:var(–gold)}
.plan-btn{display:block;text-align:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:13px;border-radius:4px;border:1.5px solid var(–border);color:var(–ink-mid);background:transparent;transition:all .2s,transform .1s;cursor:pointer;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;width:100%}
.plan-btn:hover{background:var(–navy);color:#fff;border-color:var(–navy)}
.plan-btn:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
.plan.pop .plan-btn{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk);border-color:var(–gold);font-weight:800}
.plan.pop .plan-btn:hover{background:var(–gold-hov);border-color:var(–gold-hov);color:#fff}
.packs{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px}
.pack{border-radius:8px;padding:36px 32px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:transform .3s,box-shadow .3s}
.pack:hover{transform:translateY(-4px)}
.pack-stone{background:var(–surface);border:1.5px solid var(–border)}
.pack-stone:hover{box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.08);border-color:var(–silver)}
.pack-stone::before{content:’’;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(–silver)}
.pack-prem{background:var(–navy-dk);border:1.5px solid var(–navy-dk)}
.pack-prem:hover{box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(28,58,122,.3)}
.pack-prem::before{content:’’;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–navy),var(–gold))}
.pack-badge{display:inline-block;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:20px}
.pack-stone .pack-badge{background:var(–silver-bg);color:var(–silver);border:1px solid rgba(138,150,168,.3)}
.pack-prem .pack-badge{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk);font-weight:800}
.pack-name{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-bottom:6px}
.pack-stone .pack-name{color:var(–ink)}.pack-prem .pack-name{color:#fff}
.pack-price{font-size:52px;font-weight:800;line-height:1;letter-spacing:-2px;margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:3px}
.pack-stone .pack-price{color:var(–ink)}.pack-prem .pack-price{color:#fff}
.pack-price sup{font-size:22px;padding-top:8px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0}
.pack-note{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px}
.pack-stone .pack-note{color:var(–ink-mute)}.pack-prem .pack-note{color:rgba(255,255,255,.45)}
.pack-sub{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:24px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:5px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.pack-stone .pack-sub{background:var(–navy-bg);border:1px solid rgba(28,58,122,.2)}
.pack-prem .pack-sub{background:rgba(201,162,39,.12);border:1px solid rgba(201,162,39,.25)}
.sub-lbl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase}
.pack-stone .sub-lbl{color:var(–navy)}.pack-prem .sub-lbl{color:rgba(201,162,39,.85)}
.sub-price{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.5px}
.pack-stone .sub-price{color:var(–navy)}.pack-prem .sub-price{color:var(–gold-lt)}
.pack-list{list-style:none;margin-bottom:28px}
.pack-list li{font-size:13px;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px}
.pack-stone .pack-list li{color:var(–ink-mid);border-color:var(–border-l)}
.pack-prem .pack-list li{color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.pack-list li::before{content:‘→’;flex-shrink:0;font-size:11px}
.pack-stone .pack-list li::before{color:var(–navy)}.pack-prem .pack-list li::before{color:var(–gold)}
.pack-deliv{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;margin-bottom:24px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:5px}
.pack-stone .pack-deliv{background:var(–silver-bg);color:var(–silver);border:1px solid rgba(138,150,168,.2)}
.pack-prem .pack-deliv{background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12)}
.pack-btn{display:block;text-align:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:14px;border-radius:4px;transition:all .2s,transform .1s;cursor:pointer;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;width:100%}
.pack-stone .pack-btn{background:var(–navy);color:#fff;border:1.5px solid var(–navy)}
.pack-stone .pack-btn:hover{background:var(–navy-hov);border-color:var(–navy-hov)}
.pack-prem .pack-btn{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk);border:1.5px solid var(–gold);font-weight:800}
.pack-prem .pack-btn:hover{background:var(–gold-hov);border-color:var(–gold-hov);color:#fff}

/* ══ HOW IT WORKS ══ */
.hiw{padding:112px 56px;background:var(–surface);border-top:1px solid var(–border)}
.hiw-lay{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:start;margin-top:56px}
.step{display:flex;gap:22px;position:relative}
.step:not(:last-child)::after{content:’’;position:absolute;left:19px;top:42px;width:1px;height:100%;background:var(–border-l)}
.step-n{width:40px;height:40px;flex-shrink:0;border:1.5px solid var(–border);background:var(–surface);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(–ink-mute);transition:all .25s;position:relative;z-index:1;border-radius:50%}
.step:hover .step-n{background:var(–navy);color:#fff;border-color:var(–navy)}
.step-body{padding-bottom:44px}
.step-ttl{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(–ink)}
.step-desc{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;color:var(–ink-mid)}
.hiw-panel{background:var(–navy-dk);padding:40px;border-radius:10px;position:sticky;top:calc(var(–nav-h)+24px);overflow:hidden}
.hiw-panel::before{content:’’;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–navy),var(–gold))}
.panel-lbl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);margin-bottom:28px}
.key-disp{text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px}
.key-ico{font-size:48px;display:block;margin-bottom:14px;animation:keyBeat 4s ease-in-out infinite}
.key-code{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:13px 20px;display:inline-block;border-radius:4px}
.panel-list{list-style:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07)}
.panel-list li{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4)}
.panel-list li::before{content:‘✓’;color:var(–gold);flex-shrink:0;font-weight:700}

/* ══ TESTIMONIAL ══ */
.testi{padding:96px 56px;background:var(–bg);border-top:1px solid var(–border)}
.testi-in{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center}
.tmark{font-size:64px;font-weight:700;color:var(–gold);opacity:.25;line-height:.8;margin-bottom:12px;display:block}
.tquote{font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,24px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.65;color:var(–ink);margin-bottom:32px}
.tsep{width:32px;height:2px;background:var(–gold);margin:0 auto 24px;opacity:.6}
.tauthor{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;justify-content:center}
.tav{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:var(–navy);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.tinfo strong{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(–ink)}
.tinfo span{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(–ink-mute)}

/* ══ CTA ══ */
.cta-sec{padding:128px 56px;background:var(–navy-dk);text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.cta-wm{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);font-size:22vw;font-weight:800;color:rgba(255,255,255,.03);white-space:nowrap;pointer-events:none;user-select:none;letter-spacing:-4px}
.cta-sec .s-over{justify-content:center;color:rgba(201,162,39,.7);margin-bottom:18px}
.cta-sec .s-over::before{background:var(–gold);opacity:.5}
.cta-sec h2{font-size:clamp(30px,3.8vw,60px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-2px;color:#fff;margin-bottom:18px;position:relative}
.cta-sec h2 em{font-style:normal;color:var(–gold)}
.cta-sec p{font-size:14px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);max-width:420px;margin:0 auto 44px;line-height:1.7;position:relative}
.cta-btns{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;position:relative}
.btn-lt{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–navy-dk);background:#fff;padding:15px 32px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;transition:background .2s,color .2s,transform .1s;cursor:pointer;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;border:none}
.btn-lt:hover{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk)}
.btn-out-lt{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);background:transparent;padding:15px 28px;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .2s}
.btn-out-lt:hover{border-color:#fff;color:#fff}

/* ══ CONTACT ══ */
.contact{padding:112px 56px;border-top:1px solid var(–border);background:var(–surface)}
.contact-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:start}
.cinfo p{font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;color:var(–ink-mid);margin:16px 0 28px}
.cdet{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:13px;color:var(–ink-mid);margin-bottom:12px}
.cdet .ico{color:var(–navy);font-size:16px;flex-shrink:0}
.ff{margin-bottom:20px;position:relative}
.flbl{display:block;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–ink-mute);margin-bottom:7px}
.finp,.fsel{width:100%;background:var(–bg);border:1.5px solid var(–border);color:var(–ink);font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;font-size:14px;padding:11px 13px;outline:none;-webkit-appearance:none;border-radius:5px;transition:border-color .2s}
.finp:focus,.fsel:focus{border-color:var(–navy)}
.finp::placeholder{color:var(–ink-lt);font-size:13px}
.scan{position:absolute;top:-1px;left:0;height:1.5px;width:0;background:var(–gold);border-radius:2px;pointer-events:none;z-index:2}
.finp:focus~.scan,.fsel:focus~.scan{animation:scanKey .2s ease forwards}
@keyframes scanKey{from{width:0;opacity:1}to{width:100%;opacity:.5}}
.fsub{width:100%;background:var(–navy);color:#fff;border:none;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:16px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:6px;border-radius:5px;transition:background .2s,transform .1s}
.fsub:hover{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk)}
.fsub:disabled{opacity:.5;cursor:not-allowed}
.fnote{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(–ink-lt);margin-top:13px;text-align:center;line-height:1.6}
#ferr{display:none;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:11px;color:#900;margin-bottom:14px;padding:11px 13px;background:#fff0f0;border:1px solid rgba(150,0,0,.2);border-radius:4px}
#fok{display:none;text-align:center;padding:48px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:8px;background:var(–bg)}
.ok-ico{font-size:48px;margin-bottom:16px}
.ok-ttl{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(–ink)}
.ok-sub{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(–ink-mute);line-height:1.8}

/* ══ FOOTER ══ */
footer{background:var(–navy-dk);padding:32px 56px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
.flogo{font-size:14px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none}
.flogo em{font-style:normal;color:var(–gold)}
.fcopy{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);letter-spacing:1px}
.flinks{display:flex;gap:24px;list-style:none}
.flinks a{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s}
.flinks a:hover{color:#fff}

/* ══ REVEAL ══ */
.rv{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:opacity .7s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1),transform .7s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1)}
.rv.in{opacity:1;transform:none}
.rvl{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-22px);transition:opacity .7s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1),transform .7s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1)}
.rvl.in{opacity:1;transform:none}

/* ══ KEYFRAMES ══ */
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
@keyframes floatY{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateY(-8px)}}
@keyframes marquee{from{transform:translateX(0)}to{transform:translateX(-50%)}}
@keyframes keyBeat{0%,100%{transform:scale(1) rotate(-3deg)}50%{transform:scale(1.06) rotate(3deg)}}

/* ════════════════════════════════════════════
PAGE DE PAIEMENT PLEIN ÉCRAN
════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.pay-page{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(–bg);z-index:1000;overflow-y:auto}
.pay-page.open{display:block;animation:ppIn .3s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1)}
@keyframes ppIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

/* Barre nav paiement */
.pay-nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;background:var(–bg);border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);padding:0 40px;height:60px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px}
.pay-nav-logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–navy);text-decoration:none;flex-shrink:0}
.pay-nav-logo em{font-style:normal;color:var(–gold)}
.pay-nav-secure{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(–ink-lt)}
.pay-nav-back{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(–ink-mute);background:none;border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:4px;padding:8px 16px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;flex-shrink:0}
.pay-nav-back:hover{border-color:var(–navy);color:var(–navy)}

/* Indicateur d’étapes */
.pay-steps-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0;padding:18px 40px;background:var(–surface);border-bottom:1px solid var(–border-l)}
.pstep{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(–ink-lt);flex-shrink:0}
.pstep.active{color:var(–navy);font-weight:700}
.pstep.done{color:var(–green)}
.pstep-num{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid var(–border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;transition:all .3s}
.pstep.active .pstep-num{background:var(–navy);border-color:var(–navy);color:#fff}
.pstep.done .pstep-num{background:var(–green);border-color:var(–green);color:#fff}
.pstep-line{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(–border);margin:0 12px;min-width:24px}
.pstep.done~.pstep-line,.pstep.active~.pstep-line{background:var(–navy)}

/* Layout 2 colonnes */
.pay-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 400px;gap:0;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 40px;min-height:calc(100vh - 120px)}
.pay-left{padding:40px 48px 48px 0;border-right:1px solid var(–border)}
.pay-right{padding:40px 0 48px 40px;position:sticky;top:120px;align-self:start}

.pay-section-ttl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–navy);margin-bottom:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.pay-section-ttl::before{content:’’;width:14px;height:2px;background:var(–gold);flex-shrink:0}

/* ── ÉTAPE 1 : choix pack ── */
#step1-panel{display:block}
#step2-panel{display:none}

.pack-choice-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:28px}
.pack-choice{border:2px solid var(–border);border-radius:8px;padding:22px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s;background:var(–surface);position:relative;text-align:left}
.pack-choice:hover{border-color:var(–navy);background:var(–navy-bg)}
.pack-choice.selected{border-color:var(–navy);background:var(–navy-bg)}
.pack-choice.selected::after{content:‘✓’;position:absolute;top:12px;right:12px;width:22px;height:22px;background:var(–navy);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;line-height:22px;text-align:center}
.pack-choice-badge{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:10px;display:inline-block}
.pc-stone .pack-choice-badge{background:var(–silver-bg);color:var(–silver)}
.pc-prem .pack-choice-badge{background:var(–gold-pale);color:var(–gold-dk)}
.pack-choice-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(–ink);margin-bottom:4px}
.pack-choice-price{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:var(–navy);letter-spacing:-1px;margin-bottom:4px}
.pack-choice-price sup{font-size:13px;font-weight:500}
.pack-choice-delay{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–ink-mute);letter-spacing:1px}

.sub-choice-ttl{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(–ink);margin-bottom:12px}
.sub-choice-grid{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:32px}
.sub-choice{border:2px solid var(–border);border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s;background:var(–surface);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;position:relative}
.sub-choice:hover{border-color:var(–navy);background:var(–navy-bg)}
.sub-choice.selected{border-color:var(–navy);background:var(–navy-bg)}
.sub-choice.selected::after{content:‘✓’;width:20px;height:20px;background:var(–navy);border-radius:50%;color:#fff;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;line-height:20px;text-align:center}
.sub-choice-pop{border-color:var(–gold)!important}
.sub-choice-pop .sch-name::after{content:‘Populaire’;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px;margin-left:8px;font-weight:800}
.sch-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(–ink)}
.sch-agents{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–ink-mute);letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:2px}
.sch-price{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:var(–navy);letter-spacing:-1px;flex-shrink:0}
.sch-price sup{font-size:11px;font-weight:500}
.sch-price small{font-size:11px;font-weight:300;color:var(–ink-mute)}

.step1-next{width:100%;background:var(–navy);color:#fff;border:none;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:17px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:6px;transition:background .2s,transform .1s}
.step1-next:hover{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk)}
.step1-next:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
.step1-next:disabled{opacity:.4;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none}

/* ── ÉTAPE 2 : paiement ── */
.pay-tabs{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:28px}
.pay-tab{padding:14px 18px;border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(–ink-mute);background:var(–surface);transition:all .2s;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif}
.pay-tab:hover{border-color:var(–navy);color:var(–navy);background:var(–navy-bg)}
.pay-tab.active{border-color:var(–navy);background:var(–navy-bg);color:var(–navy);font-weight:700}
.pay-tab.active .tab-ico-wrap{background:var(–navy);color:#fff}
.tab-ico-wrap{width:32px;height:32px;background:var(–bg);border-radius:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;flex-shrink:0;transition:background .2s,color .2s}
.tab-label strong{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:1px}
.tab-label span{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–ink-lt);letter-spacing:1px}

#panel-paypal{display:block}
#panel-card{display:none}
.pp-info{background:var(–navy-bg);border:1px solid rgba(28,58,122,.15);border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;font-size:13px;color:var(–ink-mid);line-height:1.6}
.pp-info-ico{font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
#paypal-btn-container{min-height:55px}

.cf-lbl{display:block;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–ink-mute);margin-bottom:8px;margin-top:20px}
.cf-lbl:first-child{margin-top:0}
.card-field{height:48px;background:var(–surface);border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:6px;padding:0 14px;transition:border-color .2s}
.card-field.card-field-invalid{border-color:var(–red)}
.card-field.card-field-valid{border-color:var(–green)}
.cf-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px}
.card-name-inp{width:100%;height:48px;background:var(–surface);border:1.5px solid var(–border);color:var(–ink);font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;font-size:14px;padding:0 14px;outline:none;border-radius:6px;transition:border-color .2s}
.card-name-inp:focus{border-color:var(–navy)}
.card-name-inp::placeholder{color:var(–ink-lt)}
#card-pay-btn{width:100%;background:var(–navy);color:#fff;border:none;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:17px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:6px;transition:background .2s,transform .1s;margin-top:24px}
#card-pay-btn:hover{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk)}
#card-pay-btn:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
#card-pay-btn:disabled{opacity:.5;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none}
#pay-error{display:none;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(–red);background:var(–red-bg);border:1px solid rgba(192,57,43,.2);padding:12px 14px;border-radius:5px;margin-top:14px}
.secure-badges{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:20px;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid var(–border-l)}
.secure-badge{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–ink-lt);letter-spacing:1px}
.step2-back{background:none;border:none;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(–ink-mute);cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:20px;padding:0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;transition:color .2s}
.step2-back:hover{color:var(–navy)}

/* ── Colonne droite récap ── */
.recap-card{background:var(–surface);border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:16px}
.recap-card-top{background:var(–navy-dk);padding:22px 24px;position:relative}
.recap-card-top::after{content:’’;position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–navy),var(–gold))}
.recap-plan-name{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);margin-bottom:5px}
.recap-plan-ttl{font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-bottom:2px}
.recap-plan-sub{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);font-weight:300}
.recap-lines{padding:18px 22px}
.recap-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border-l);font-size:13px}
.recap-row:last-child{border:none;padding-top:12px;margin-top:4px}
.recap-row .rl{color:var(–ink-mid)}.recap-row .rv{font-weight:600;color:var(–ink)}
.recap-total .rl{font-weight:700;color:var(–ink)}
.recap-total .rv{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:var(–navy);letter-spacing:-.5px}
.recap-note{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–ink-lt);padding:0 22px 16px;letter-spacing:1px}
.trust-items{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.trust-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:13px;color:var(–ink-mid);padding:10px 14px;background:var(–surface);border:1px solid var(–border-l);border-radius:6px}
.trust-ico{font-size:15px;flex-shrink:0}

/* ════════════════════════════════════════════
PAGE SUCCÈS
════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.success-page{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(–surface);z-index:2000;overflow-y:auto;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:40px 24px;text-align:center}
.success-page.show{display:flex}
.success-anim{font-size:72px;margin-bottom:20px;animation:popIn .5s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1)}
@keyframes popIn{from{transform:scale(0)}to{transform:scale(1)}}
.success-badge{background:var(–navy);color:#fff;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:20px;display:inline-block}
.success-ttl{font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,42px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-2px;color:var(–ink);margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.1}
.success-ttl em{font-style:normal;color:var(–gold)}
.success-sub{font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;color:var(–ink-mid);max-width:480px;margin-bottom:32px}
.success-detail{background:var(–bg);border:1px solid var(–border);border-radius:10px;padding:24px 28px;max-width:440px;width:100%;margin-bottom:28px;text-align:left;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.success-detail::before{content:’’;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–navy),var(–gold))}
.success-detail-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border-l);font-size:13px}
.success-detail-row:last-child{border:none}
.success-detail-row span:first-child{color:var(–ink-mute)}
.success-detail-row span:last-child{font-weight:600;color:var(–ink)}
.success-steps{max-width:440px;width:100%;margin-bottom:32px;text-align:left}
.success-step{display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:14px}
.ss-num{width:28px;height:28px;background:var(–navy-bg);border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(–navy);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
.ss-body strong{display:block;color:var(–ink);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:2px;font-size:14px}
.ss-body p{font-size:13px;color:var(–ink-mid);margin:0;line-height:1.6}
.success-btn{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fff;background:var(–navy);padding:15px 36px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;transition:background .2s;cursor:pointer;border:none;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif}
.success-btn:hover{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk)}

/* ════════════════════════════════════════════
PAGE GESTION ABONNEMENT (lien email renouvellement)
════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.renew-page{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(–bg);z-index:3000;overflow-y:auto}
.renew-page.show{display:block;animation:ppIn .3s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1)}
.renew-nav{height:60px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 40px;background:var(–bg);border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10}
.renew-nav-logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–navy);text-decoration:none}
.renew-nav-logo em{font-style:normal;color:var(–gold)}
.renew-close{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(–ink-mute);background:none;border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:4px;padding:8px 16px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.renew-close:hover{border-color:var(–navy);color:var(–navy)}
.renew-body{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 24px}
.renew-hero{margin-bottom:40px}
.renew-key{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(–navy);background:var(–navy-bg);border:1px solid rgba(28,58,122,.2);padding:10px 20px;display:inline-block;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:16px}
.renew-hero h2{font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,36px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1.5px;color:var(–ink);margin-bottom:8px}
.renew-hero h2 em{font-style:normal;color:var(–gold)}
.renew-hero p{font-size:14px;color:var(–ink-mid);line-height:1.7}
.renew-current{background:var(–surface);border:1.5px solid var(–border);border-radius:10px;padding:24px 28px;margin-bottom:32px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px}
.rc-label{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–ink-mute);margin-bottom:6px}
.rc-val{font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:var(–ink);letter-spacing:-.5px}
.rc-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:var(–green-bg);color:var(–green);font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:700}
.rc-badge.warn{background:var(–gold-pale);color:var(–gold-dk)}

.renew-section-ttl{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–navy);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.renew-section-ttl::before{content:’’;width:14px;height:2px;background:var(–gold);flex-shrink:0}

/* Options renouvellement */
.renew-options{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:28px}
.renew-opt{border:2px solid var(–border);border-radius:8px;padding:18px 22px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:var(–surface);transition:all .25s;position:relative}
.renew-opt:hover{border-color:var(–navy);background:var(–navy-bg)}
.renew-opt.selected{border-color:var(–navy);background:var(–navy-bg)}
.renew-opt.selected::after{content:‘✓’;width:22px;height:22px;background:var(–navy);border-radius:50%;color:#fff;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;line-height:22px;text-align:center}
.renew-opt.current-plan{border-color:var(–gold)}
.renew-opt.current-plan .ro-name::after{content:‘Votre formule actuelle’;font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(–gold-pale);color:var(–gold-dk);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px;margin-left:10px}
.ro-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(–ink)}
.ro-agents{font-family:‘DM Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–ink-mute);letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:2px}
.ro-price{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:var(–navy);letter-spacing:-1px;flex-shrink:0}
.ro-price sup{font-size:11px;font-weight:500}
.ro-price small{font-size:11px;font-weight:300;color:var(–ink-mute)}

.renew-pay-btn{width:100%;background:var(–navy);color:#fff;border:none;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:17px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:6px;transition:background .2s,transform .1s;margin-bottom:12px}
.renew-pay-btn:hover{background:var(–gold);color:var(–navy-dk)}
.renew-pay-btn:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
.renew-pay-btn:disabled{opacity:.4;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none}
#renew-paypal-container{min-height:55px;margin-bottom:20px}

/* Résiliation */
.resil-zone{border:1.5px solid rgba(192,57,43,.2);border-radius:8px;padding:22px;background:var(–red-bg);margin-top:40px}
.resil-ttl{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(–red);margin-bottom:6px}
.resil-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(–ink-mid);margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.6}
.resil-btn{background:none;border:1.5px solid var(–red);color:var(–red);font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.resil-btn:hover{background:var(–red);color:#fff}
.resil-confirm{display:none;margin-top:14px}
.resil-confirm p{font-size:13px;color:var(–ink-mid);margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.6}
.resil-confirm-btns{display:flex;gap:10px}
.resil-yes{background:var(–red);color:#fff;border:none;font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;transition:background .2s}
.resil-yes:hover{background:#a93226}
.resil-no{background:none;border:1.5px solid var(–border);color:var(–ink-mute);font-family:‘Inter’,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.resil-no:hover{border-color:var(–navy);color:var(–navy)}

/* ══ RESPONSIVE ══ */
@media(max-width:1024px){
nav,footer{padding-left:32px;padding-right:32px}
.hero,.features,.proof,.pricing,.hiw,.testi,.cta-sec,.contact{padding-left:32px;padding-right:32px}
.feats{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
.proof-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
.plans{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
.packs{grid-template-columns:1fr}
.hiw-lay{gap:48px}
.pay-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr}
.pay-right{display:none}
.pay-left{border-right:none;padding-right:0}
}
@media(max-width:767px){
:root{–nav-h:56px}
nav{padding:0 20px}
.nav-links,.nav-cta{display:none}
.burger{display:flex}
.hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:calc(var(–nav-h)+36px) 20px 48px;gap:0;min-height:auto}
.hero-right,.hero-grid{display:none}
.hero-acts{flex-direction:column;align-items:stretch;gap:10px}
.btn-main,.btn-out{text-align:center;width:100%;padding:15px 20px}
.features,.proof,.pricing,.hiw,.testi,.cta-sec,.contact{padding:64px 20px}
.feats{grid-template-columns:1fr}
.proof-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
.proof-item{padding:28px 12px}
.proof-n{font-size:40px}
.plans{grid-template-columns:1fr}
.packs{grid-template-columns:1fr}
.hiw-lay{grid-template-columns:1fr}
.hiw-panel{display:none}
.cta-btns{flex-direction:column;align-items:stretch}
.btn-lt,.btn-out-lt{text-align:center;width:100%;padding:15px 20px}
.contact-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:44px}
footer{flex-direction:column;gap:16px;text-align:center;padding:24px 20px}
.flinks{flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}
.pay-nav,.pay-steps-bar{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px}
.pay-layout{padding:0 20px}
.pack-choice-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
.cf-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}
.renew-nav,.renew-body{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px}
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div id="cur"></div><div id="cur-ring"></div><div id="heartbeat"></div>

<!-- ══ NAV ══ -->

<nav id="nav">
  <a href="#top" class="logo">Starck<em>Key</em></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#features">Fonctionnalités</a></li>
    <li><a href="#pricing">Tarifs</a></li>
    <li><a href="#hiw">Mise en place</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#pricing" class="nav-cta">Souscrire maintenant</a>
  <button class="burger" id="burger" aria-label="Menu" onclick="toggleMenu()"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
</nav>
<div class="mob-menu" id="mobMenu">
  <a href="#features" onclick="closeMob()">Fonctionnalités</a>
  <a href="#pricing" onclick="closeMob()">Tarifs</a>
  <a href="#hiw" onclick="closeMob()">Mise en place</a>
  <a href="#contact" onclick="closeMob()">Contact</a>
  <a href="#pricing" class="mob-cta" onclick="closeMob()">Souscrire maintenant</a>
</div>

<!-- ══ HERO ══ -->

<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-over">Solution SaaS Immobilier</div>
    <h1>Vos agents,<br><em>organisés.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-body">StarckKey centralise les agendas de tous vos agents immobiliers en un seul tableau de bord. Planifiez, coordonnez, performez — sans friction.</p>
    <div class="hero-acts">
      <button class="btn-main" onclick="openPay('abonnement')">Démarrer maintenant</button>
      <a href="#features" class="btn-out">Voir les fonctionnalités →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="fl-badge fl-1"><span class="fl-icon">✓</span><div class="fl-text"><strong>Déploiement 24–48h</strong><span>Pack Premium</span></div></div>
    <div class="hcard">
      <div class="card-lbl">Tableau de bord — Agence Prestige</div>
      <div class="card-agent"><div class="av">S</div><div><div class="ag-name">Sophie Martin</div><div class="ag-role">Agent Senior · 12 mandats actifs</div></div></div>
      <div class="cstats">
        <div class="sbox"><div class="sv">8<span> rdv</span></div><div class="slbl">Cette semaine</div></div>
        <div class="sbox"><div class="sv">94<span> %</span></div><div class="slbl">Taux présence</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sched-ttl">Agenda du jour</div>
      <div class="sched-row"><div class="sdot da"></div><div class="stime">09:30</div><div class="stxt">Visite — Rue de Rivoli</div><span class="sbadge bok">Confirmé</span></div>
      <div class="sched-row"><div class="sdot db"></div><div class="stime">11:00</div><div class="stxt">Signature compromis</div><span class="sbadge bok">Confirmé</span></div>
      <div class="sched-row"><div class="sdot dc"></div><div class="stime">15:30</div><div class="stxt">Estimation — Le Marais</div><span class="sbadge bpend">En attente</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="fl-badge fl-2"><span class="fl-icon">🔑</span><div class="fl-text"><strong>Clé activée</strong><span>SK-4821-XXXX</span></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ MARQUEE ══ -->

<div class="mq-wrap"><div class="mq-track">
  <span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Gestion d'agenda</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Planification intelligente</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Accès sécurisé</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Dashboard Direction</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Rappels automatiques</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Déploiement 48h</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Gestion d'agenda</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Planification intelligente</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Accès sécurisé</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Dashboard Direction</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Rappels automatiques</span><span class="mq-item"><span>/</span>Déploiement 48h</span>
</div></div>

<!-- ══ FEATURES ══ -->

<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="s-head rv"><div class="s-over">Fonctionnalités</div><h2 class="s-title">Tout ce dont votre<br>agence a <em>besoin.</em></h2></div>
  <div class="feats">
    <div class="feat rv"><div class="feat-bar"></div><div class="feat-num">01</div><div class="feat-ico">📅</div><div class="feat-ttl">Agenda centralisé</div><p class="feat-desc">Visualisez les disponibilités de tous vos agents en temps réel. Finis les conflits de planning.</p></div>
    <div class="feat rv" style="transition-delay:.06s"><div class="feat-bar"></div><div class="feat-num">02</div><div class="feat-ico">🔑</div><div class="feat-ttl">Accès sécurisé</div><p class="feat-desc">Chaque agent dispose d'une clé d'accès personnelle renouvelable. La Direction contrôle tout.</p></div>
    <div class="feat rv" style="transition-delay:.12s"><div class="feat-bar"></div><div class="feat-num">03</div><div class="feat-ico">📊</div><div class="feat-ttl">Dashboard Direction</div><p class="feat-desc">Vue globale sur l'activité de l'équipe. Suivi de charge, performances et statistiques en temps réel.</p></div>
    <div class="feat rv" style="transition-delay:.18s"><div class="feat-bar"></div><div class="feat-num">04</div><div class="feat-ico">🔔</div><div class="feat-ttl">Rappels automatiques</div><p class="feat-desc">SMS et emails envoyés avant chaque rendez-vous. Réduction drastique des oublis clients.</p></div>
    <div class="feat rv" style="transition-delay:.24s"><div class="feat-bar"></div><div class="feat-num">05</div><div class="feat-ico">👥</div><div class="feat-ttl">Gestion d'équipe</div><p class="feat-desc">Ajoutez vos agents en quelques secondes. Droits différenciés selon le rôle de chacun.</p></div>
    <div class="feat rv" style="transition-delay:.3s"><div class="feat-bar"></div><div class="feat-num">06</div><div class="feat-ico">🔄</div><div class="feat-ttl">Renouvellement simplifié</div><p class="feat-desc">Rappel automatique 30 jours avant expiration. Renouvelez, montez en gamme ou ajoutez des agents en un clic.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ PROOF ══ -->

<section class="proof">
  <div class="proof-hd rv"><div class="s-over">StarckKey en chiffres</div></div>
  <div class="proof-grid">
    <div class="proof-item rv"><span class="proof-n" data-target="48">0</span><span class="proof-lbl">Heures déploiement</span><div class="proof-bar"></div></div>
    <div class="proof-item rv" style="transition-delay:.08s"><span class="proof-n" data-target="100">0</span><span class="proof-lbl">% Cloud · 0 install</span><div class="proof-bar"></div></div>
    <div class="proof-item rv" style="transition-delay:.16s"><span class="proof-n" data-target="3">0</span><span class="proof-lbl">Formules d'accès</span><div class="proof-bar"></div></div>
    <div class="proof-item rv" style="transition-delay:.24s"><span class="proof-n" data-suffix="h">24</span><span class="proof-lbl">Support réactif</span><div class="proof-bar"></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ PRICING ══ -->

<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
  <div class="rv">
    <div class="s-over">Tarifs</div>
    <h2 class="s-title">Simple, transparent,<br><em>sans surprise.</em></h2>
    <p class="pricing-sub">Deux composantes : un <strong>abonnement mensuel</strong> pour l'accès à la plateforme, et un <strong>pack d'installation unique</strong> pour le déploiement. Les deux s'achètent en une seule fois.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="plbl rv">Abonnements mensuels — Accès à la plateforme</div>
  <div class="plans">
    <div class="plan rv">
      <div class="plan-tag">Solo</div>
      <div class="plan-price"><sup>€</sup>49<small>,99</small></div>
      <div class="plan-per">par mois · jusqu'à 3 agents</div>
      <ul class="plan-feats"><li>3 agents inclus</li><li>Agenda individuel</li><li>Rappels email automatiques</li><li>Renouvellement en 1 clic</li><li>Support standard</li></ul>
      <button class="plan-btn" onclick="openPay('abonnement','Solo')">Souscrire — 49,99 €/mois</button>
    </div>
    <div class="plan pop rv" style="transition-delay:.1s">
      <div class="plan-tag">Agence</div>
      <div class="plan-price"><sup>€</sup>199<small>,99</small></div>
      <div class="plan-per">par mois · jusqu'à 10 agents</div>
      <ul class="plan-feats"><li>10 agents inclus</li><li>Dashboard Direction</li><li>Rapports de performance</li><li>Rappels SMS + email</li><li>Renouvellement / upgrade</li><li>Support prioritaire</li></ul>
      <button class="plan-btn" onclick="openPay('abonnement','Agence')">Souscrire — 199,99 €/mois</button>
    </div>
    <div class="plan rv" style="transition-delay:.2s">
      <div class="plan-tag">Grand Compte</div>
      <div class="plan-price"><sup>€</sup>499<small>,99</small></div>
      <div class="plan-per">par mois · agents illimités</div>
      <ul class="plan-feats"><li>Agents illimités</li><li>Multi-agences</li><li>API &amp; intégrations</li><li>Onboarding personnalisé</li><li>Account manager dédié</li></ul>
      <button class="plan-btn" onclick="openPay('abonnement','Grand Compte')">Souscrire — 499,99 €/mois</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="plbl rv">Packs d'installation — Frais uniques de déploiement</div>
  <div class="packs">
    <div class="pack pack-stone rv">
      <div class="pack-badge">Pack Stone</div>
      <div class="pack-name">Installation Standard</div>
      <div class="pack-price"><sup>€</sup>1 200</div>
      <div class="pack-note">Frais uniques · + abonnement mensuel au choix</div>
      <div class="pack-sub"><span class="sub-lbl">Abonnement inclus dans le choix</span></div>
      <ul class="pack-list"><li>Configuration complète de votre instance</li><li>Création des comptes agents</li><li>Formation de prise en main</li><li>Migration des données existantes</li><li>Support dédié durant le déploiement</li></ul>
      <div class="pack-deliv"><span>🗓</span>&nbsp;Délai : sous 10 jours ouvrés</div>
      <button class="pack-btn" onclick="openPay('pack','Stone')">Choisir Pack Stone + Abonnement</button>
    </div>
    <div class="pack pack-prem rv" style="transition-delay:.1s">
      <div class="pack-badge">Pack Premium</div>
      <div class="pack-name">Installation Prioritaire</div>
      <div class="pack-price"><sup>€</sup>1 800</div>
      <div class="pack-note">Frais uniques · + abonnement mensuel au choix</div>
      <div class="pack-sub"><span class="sub-lbl">Abonnement inclus dans le choix</span></div>
      <ul class="pack-list"><li>Tout le Pack Stone inclus</li><li>Déploiement en urgence — priorité absolue</li><li>Paramétrage avancé sur mesure</li><li>Formation approfondie équipe + direction</li><li>Support téléphonique dédié 30 jours</li></ul>
      <div class="pack-deliv"><span>⚡</span>&nbsp;Délai : 24 à 48 heures</div>
      <button class="pack-btn" onclick="openPay('pack','Premium')">Choisir Pack Premium + Abonnement</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ HOW IT WORKS ══ -->

<section class="hiw" id="hiw">
  <div class="s-head rv"><div class="s-over">Mise en place</div><h2 class="s-title">Opérationnel en<br><em>48 heures.</em></h2></div>
  <div class="hiw-lay">
    <div>
      <div class="step rv"><div class="step-n">01</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-ttl">Vous choisissez votre formule</div><p class="step-desc">Sélectionnez votre pack d'installation et votre abonnement mensuel. Paiement sécurisé en une seule fois.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step rv" style="transition-delay:.08s"><div class="step-n">02</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-ttl">On configure votre instance</div><p class="step-desc">Création des profils agents, paramétrage des droits d'accès, personnalisation de votre tableau de bord.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step rv" style="transition-delay:.16s"><div class="step-n">03</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-ttl">Vos agents reçoivent leurs clés</div><p class="step-desc">Chaque agent reçoit sa clé d'accès personnelle par email. Connexion immédiate depuis n'importe quel navigateur.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step rv" style="transition-delay:.24s"><div class="step-n">04</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-ttl">Renouvellement automatique tous les 30 jours</div><p class="step-desc">Un email vous rappelle l'échéance. Renouvelez, montez en gamme ou ajoutez des agents en un clic depuis votre espace client.</p></div></div>
    </div>
